<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.2.5">
<l>tōḷicēr piṉṉai poruṭṭeru tēḻtaḻīik</l>
<l>kōḷiyār kōvala ṉārkkuṭak kūttaṉār</l>
<l>tāḷiṇai mēlaṇi taṇṇantu ḻāyeṉṟē</l>
<l>nāḷunā ṇaikiṉṟa tāleṉṟaṉ mātarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“The cool Tulsi [that is the] decoration on the foot-pair</l>
<l>of him who danced the pot dance of the cowherds, the receiver,</l>
<l>embracing seven bulls for Piṉṉai’s sake, to join her with [pretty] shoulders,”</l>
<l>thus day by day languishes my girl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
